prodNameC: 常盈 無需選粹胰島素樣生長因子II酵素免疫試劑組
ingredientsDesc: I. Wash Concentrate: containing buffered saline with a nonionic detergent.\nJ. Stopping Solution: containing 0.2 M sulfuric acid.\n

A. Anti-IGF-II-Coated Microttitration Strips: One stripholder containing 96 microtitration wells coated with anti-IGF-II antibody.
B. IGF-II Standards: containing concentrations of approximately 0, 50, 150, 400, 800, 1500 and 2000 ng/ml IGF-II in protein-based buffer with sodium azide as a preservative.
C. IGF-II Controls: containing low and high concentrations of IGF-II in a protein-based buffer with sodium azide as a preservative.
D. IGF-II Assay Buffer: containing a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
E. IGF-II Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate: containing anti-IGF-II antibody conjugated to the enzyme horseradish peroxidase in a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
F. TMB Chromogen Solution: containing a solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) in buffer with hydrogen peroxide.
G. Sample Buffer I: containing sample buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
H. Sample Buffer II: containing sample buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
